		<title>超罕見連體嬰貓？真相曝光讓網友們笑翻 </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/21/%e8%b6%85%e7%bd%95%e8%a6%8b%e9%80%a3%e9%ab%94%e5%ac%b0%e8%b2%93%ef%bc%9f%e7%9c%9f%e7%9b%b8%e6%9b%9d%e5%85%89%e8%ae%93%e7%b6%b2%e5%8f%8b%e5%80%91%e7%ac%91%e7%bf%bb/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 洪瑜蓉]]></dc:creator>
